="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin-bottom: 28.4pt; text-indent: 66pt;"><span style="font-size: 21pt; font-family: Gabriola; color: rgb(114, 0, 16);">Contact:&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 21pt; font-family: Gabriola; color: rgb(1, 10, 57);">Please contact me as soon as auction ends if you are watching more items for combined shipping!</span><b><span style="font-size: 21pt; color: rgb(1, 24, 91);"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin-bottom: 34.65pt; text-indent: 66pt;"><span style="font-size: 21pt; font-family: Gabriola; color: rgb(1, 10, 57);">~Feedback~</span><b><span style="font-size: 21pt; color: rgb(1, 24, 91);"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin-bottom: 34.65pt; text-indent: 66pt;"><span style="font-size: 21pt; font-family: Gabriola; color: rgb(18, 26, 46);">Please let me know you have received your package and is happy with it by leaving me feedback. If you are not satisfied with your order, please contact me via email first so I can try to accommodate you before you leave me feedback!</span><b><span style="font-size: 21pt; color: rgb(1, 24, 91);"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin-bottom: 34.65pt; text-indent: 66pt;"><span style="font-size: 21pt; font-family: Gabriola; color: rgb(11, 33, 118);">~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~</span><b><span style="font-size: 21pt; color: rgb(1, 24, 91);"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin-bottom: 28.4pt; text-indent: 66pt;"><span style="font-size: 21pt; font-family: Gabriola; color: rgb(14, 21, 44);">After 6 years of helping my sister get through Nursing school with her 4 kiddos, we are now trying to pay off debt so I can go back to school and get my AA so I can pursue Law School~ I’ve been collecting stickers and Classic pooh for years and now will be liquidating a lot of my collection.</span><b><span style="font-size: 21pt; color: rgb(1, 24, 91);"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="margin: 0in 0in 21.3pt -49.5pt; text-indent: 49.5pt;"></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 21pt; font-family: Gabriola; color: rgb(14, 21, 44);">To our next adventure………</span></p></h1></div></div>')
